Content:
@Tholin FYI, for fun I put chip on top of the diagram for ceramic package that you shared. Although some Z80 wires seems to be problematically bent, maybe it is not too bad.
I don't think ceramic package is in the books for this run, but still interesting to entertain the idea.

Z80 here has a certain advantage of VDD on the sides of the chip rather than 20/40.
